<hr data-start="1552" data-end="1555">
<p data-start="1557" data-end="1580">✅ So the workflow is:</p>
<ul data-start="1581" data-end="1728">
<li data-start="1581" data-end="1616">
<p data-start="1583" data-end="1616"><strong data-start="1583" data-end="1614">Code + SQL scripts → GitHub</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-start="1617" data-end="1654">
<p data-start="1619" data-end="1654"><strong data-start="1619" data-end="1652">Actual database → stays local</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-start="1655" data-end="1728">
<p data-start="1657" data-end="1728"><code data-start="1657" data-end="1726">.gitignore → avoids pushing unnecessary libraries or compiled files</code></p>
</li>
</ul>
